            "quote_text": "In my clinic, I see the frustration that comes with reactive skin. The key is not just to soothe, but to rebuild. We must address the compromised barrier, quiet the inflammatory signals, and restore the skin's own defence mechanisms. That is the foundation of the Aliangé clinical approach — a complete system for lasting skin health.",
            "attribution": "— Dr. Alison Jamieson"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "q1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "label": "Our Approach",
        "headline": "A Clinical Approach to Calming Redness",
        "body": "<p>While many products offer a single ingredient to temporarily soothe redness, Aliangé's philosophy is to target the multiple underlying causes of inflammation simultaneously. Our approach utilises a synergistic routine of products that work together to rebuild the skin barrier, inhibit inflammatory pathways, and support a healthy microbiome.</p>",
        "bg": "white",
